{"tid":758152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府外圍機構　致函　港獨派陳國強　竭誠服務社會　行政長官頒獎","createTime":"2018-07-27T12:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T12:00:31.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4577979baa670bef68173a4fdc50aff72fef82","tid":758152,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:00:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=147093099515794&amp;set=a.110215696536868.1073741829.100026453132460&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D147093099515794%26set%3Da.110215696536868.1073741829.100026453132460%26type%3D3&d=CmYCCzSNr2JzQEY45Vq1IzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a511fe1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=147093099515794&amp;set=a.110215696536868.1073741829.100026453132460&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/hNy3Yg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FhNy3Yg&h=0567d051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKit Wan 去領獎啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃子希 恭喜你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCheuk On Ng 猛料！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJames Chan 死佐一個陳國強，還有千千萬萬個陳國強<br />\n<br />\nAntony Yuen 大陸有個男明星陳國強，做諸葛亮好出名。<br />\n<br />\n杜比 還有TVB 老闆 Charles Chan<br />\n<br />\nAntony Yuen 依個最出名，長期有班明星仔黐埋去，食都食唔晒，有料！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許銳宇 強哥 上位啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAngel Chan 收買你呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAntony Yuen 兄弟，有料！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJames Chan 大家不要玩啦，香港有千千萬萬個陳國強⋯⋯我甘多口，政府點會頒獎給我!他們幸不得要搵架大貨車車死我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRing Zit 快找記者公開向特首致謝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHon Kuen Ma 匪類組織 <a href=\"http://hkipg.org/合作機構/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkipg.org%2F%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%2F&d=CmYCCzSNr2JzQEY45Vq1IzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=030e4295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkipg.org/合作機構/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChan Man Kong 話撚知佢，問下係咪行政長官頒獎，係就去領獎。然後大嗌支持港獨"}]}